You know we were talking about unions before.

00:28:06.680 --> 00:28:10.680
I assumed they were something that became stronger a bit later on, were they?

00:28:10.680 --> 00:28:15.680
There was never a union to encompass the clothing trade.

00:28:15.680 --> 00:28:17.680
It was very difficult.

00:28:17.680 --> 00:28:20.680
It would have to be the general workers union.

00:28:20.680 --> 00:28:22.680
So not many people in those.

00:28:22.680 --> 00:28:24.680
Do you think it was something that was needed?

00:28:24.680 --> 00:28:25.680
Oh yeah.

00:28:25.680 --> 00:28:27.680
But why though?

00:28:27.680 --> 00:28:29.680
Well because it stopped.

00:28:29.680 --> 00:28:32.680
I mean I could always stick up for myself.

00:28:32.680 --> 00:28:36.680
I know, but if somebody didn't like a job they could go somewhere else, couldn't they?

00:28:36.680 --> 00:28:38.680
Yeah, it was very easy to walk.

00:28:38.680 --> 00:28:40.680
There was no trouble.

00:28:40.680 --> 00:28:47.680
Not like today, if you're unemployed you're unemployed and getting another job is, today is difficult.

00:28:47.680 --> 00:28:51.680
You could walk, you could finish on a Monday and start work on a Tuesday.

00:28:51.680 --> 00:28:54.680
So why would you need a union then?

00:28:54.680 --> 00:28:58.680
Not in those days, but it would have been useful.

00:28:58.680 --> 00:29:04.680
I didn't believe in unions when I was, my mother didn't believe in unions, you see.

00:29:04.680 --> 00:29:06.680
So I didn't believe in them.

00:29:06.680 --> 00:29:09.680
So I would never have joined a union.

00:29:09.680 --> 00:29:14.680
Plus you had to pay the union fees which you didn't want taken out of your wages.

00:29:14.680 --> 00:29:18.680
But bad enough with national health, you know.

00:29:19.680 --> 00:29:21.680
I forgot what I was going to say now.

00:29:21.680 --> 00:29:28.680
But you could say that the work the unions did was detrimental sometimes.

00:29:28.680 --> 00:29:31.680
You know, when they became quite powerful.

00:29:31.680 --> 00:29:33.680
Never in the clothing trade.

00:29:33.680 --> 00:29:38.680
I tell you what, there was a strike which is, I think, significant.

00:29:38.680 --> 00:29:41.680
And people committed suicide over it.

00:29:41.680 --> 00:29:43.680
There was a strike in the clothing trade.

00:29:43.680 --> 00:29:45.680
I was never part of it.

00:29:45.680 --> 00:29:48.680
It was years before the war.

00:29:48.680 --> 00:29:54.680
These people, and I think now when you think about it, it's very relevant today.

00:29:54.680 --> 00:30:01.680
These pile of clothing workers in the Midlands came out on strike.

00:30:01.680 --> 00:30:05.680
