It starved for a few months, didn't it, Bro?

00:31:18.680 --> 00:31:19.680
Yeah, oh yeah.

00:31:19.680 --> 00:31:21.680
And that's all the extra pay they got.

00:31:21.680 --> 00:31:27.680
So all the strike and all the suffering was for three eights.

00:31:27.680 --> 00:31:29.680
It's sad, isn't it?

00:31:29.680 --> 00:31:31.680
It is, yeah.

00:31:31.680 --> 00:31:34.680
And I think it epitomises the times then.

00:31:34.680 --> 00:31:37.680
And what the times are now.

