It's been eroded away.

00:32:20.680 --> 00:32:22.680
But it is being eroded away for everybody.

00:32:22.680 --> 00:32:24.680
They've got pensions now.

00:32:24.680 --> 00:32:28.680
And I think people who start work now are much, much worse off

00:32:28.680 --> 00:32:34.680
because they're not going to get the pensions that workers who started years ago will get.

00:32:34.680 --> 00:32:37.680
No, they've got to work till they're 70 for a start, haven't they?

00:32:37.680 --> 00:32:39.680
90 probably.

00:32:39.680 --> 00:32:40.680
By that time.

00:32:40.680 --> 00:32:42.680
By the time they get to it, yes.

